textAfterTable: Profile created on March 14, 2002. Did you know? Sean was discovered by actor Alan Rickman. Sean began acting on stage when he was five years old. He started working with the Royal Shakespeare Company when he was ten. Even though Sean's favorite sport is cycling, his contract with Warner Bros. will not allow him to ride up mountains or outside. Sean used to paly guitar in the band Crambo. His favorite dish is spaghetti carbonara. Sean owns an acre of the moon, a birthday present from a relative.
